---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base";
import aboutImg from "../assets/Matt.jpg";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
const meta = {
	title: "About",
	description: "All about me Matt üßë‚Äç‚öïÔ∏è_ü¶ñüß®",
};
export const prerender = true;
---

<PageLayout meta={meta}>
	<article class="about-page">
		<header class="about-header">
			<div class="about-image">
				<Image
					src={aboutImg}
					height={aboutImg.height}
					width={aboutImg.width}
					alt="A Photo of Matthew Deloughry looking off to the right."
					loading="eager"
					class="profile-photo"
					transition:name={"profile-image"}
				/>
			</div>
			<div class="about-intro">
				<h1 class="about-title">About</h1>
				<p class="about-subtitle">Developer, Streamer, and all-round Nerd from Sheffield</p>
			</div>
		</header>

		<div class="about-content">
			<div class="about-card">
				<p>
					Aye up, I'm Matt<strike>hew</strike> Peck-Deloughry, a web developer from Sheffield. I've been
					slinging code for nigh on 15 year now and I can tell you, I've developed a reet fondness for it.
				</p>
				<p>
					You'll mostly find me professionally using PHP and Laravel, but I like to have a bit of fun
					with JavaScript, TypeScript, and Deno too. There's nowt I love more than creating a problem
					and then figuring out how to fix it with a bit of code. It's like a reet good puzzle!
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="about-card">
				<p>
					I've worked on all sorts of projects in my time, big and small, and I always approach each one
					with the same level of excitement. I'm always looking to learn new things and improve my
					skills, and I love nothing more than bringing ideas to life through code.
				</p>
				<p>
					But it's not just about the code for me. It's about making things, having a bit of fun, and
					always looking for new challenges.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="about-card">
				<p>
					Oh, and if you're up for it, you can catch me streaming my coding adventures on Twitch. It's a
					bit of a hoot, if I do say so meself!
				</p>
				<p class="disclaimer">
					<small
						>Disclaimer: Above was generated by AI, asking to write a blurb for sheffield coder and
						nerd, born and bred!</small>
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="about-card">
				<p>
					But really I think this sums me up perfectly, I love the challenge of using some language I
					love to solve something, finding the pit-falls and ways out of those said holes Finding
					solutions to problems is what it's all about - using all my "hacks" and "lessons" to produce a
					comprehensive solution..
				</p>
				<p>
					I try to share that enthusiasm in everything I do, from mentoring and streaming to just
					chatting with people. When you love what you do, it makes everything more fun and rewarding.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="about-quote">
				<p class="quote-text">
					As I say <span class="quote-highlight"
						>"Av' fun developing, Av' fun learning, then Av'a crack at engineering it!"</span>
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</article>

	<style>
		.about-page {
			max-width: 1000px;
			margin: 0 auto;
			padding: 2rem;
		}

		.about-header {
			display: flex;
			align-items: flex-start;
			gap: 2rem;
			margin-bottom: 4rem;
			padding-bottom: 2rem;
			border-bottom: 2px solid var(--theme-accent);
		}

		.about-image {
			flex-shrink: 0;
			width: 300px;
			height: 300px;
		}

		.profile-photo {
			width: 100%;
			height: 100%;
			border-radius: 12px;
			object-fit: cover;
			transition: transform 0.3s ease;
			filter: grayscale(100%);
		}

		.profile-photo:hover {
			transform: scale(1.02);
			filter: grayscale(0%);
		}

		.about-intro {
			flex: 1;
			text-align: left;
		}

		.about-title {
			font-size: 3rem;
			font-weight: 700;
			margin-bottom: 1rem;
			color: var(--theme-text);
			font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
			text-transform: uppercase;
			letter-spacing: 1px;
		}

		.about-subtitle {
			font-size: 1.2rem;
			color: var(--theme-quote);
			font-style: italic;
			margin: 0;
		}

		.about-content {
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			gap: 2rem;
		}

		.about-card {
			background: var(--theme-bg);
			padding: 2rem;
			border-radius: 12px;
		}

		.about-card p {
			font-size: 1.1rem;
			line-height: 1.7;
			color: var(--theme-text);
			margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
		}

		.about-card p:last-child {
			margin-bottom: 0;
		}

		.disclaimer {
			font-weight: bold;
			color: var(--theme-accent);
		}

		.about-quote {
			background: var(--theme-bg);
			padding: 3rem;
			border-radius: 12px;
			text-align: center;
			border-left: 4px solid var(--theme-accent);
		}

		.quote-text {
			font-size: 1.3rem;
			line-height: 1.6;
			color: var(--theme-text);
			margin: 0;
			font-style: italic;
		}

		.quote-highlight {
			font-weight: bold;
			color: var(--theme-accent);
		}

		@media (max-width: 1024px) {
			.about-header {
				flex-direction: column;
				align-items: center;
				text-align: center;
			}

			.about-image {
				width: 200px;
				height: 200px;
			}

			.about-intro {
				text-align: center;
			}
		}

		@media (max-width: 768px) {
			.about-page {
				padding: 1rem;
			}

			.about-title {
				font-size: 2rem;
			}

			.about-card {
				padding: 1.5rem;
			}

			.about-quote {
				padding: 2rem;
			}

			.quote-text {
				font-size: 1.1rem;
			}
		}
	</style>
</PageLayout>
